    "html": "<DOCUMENT>\n<TYPE>EX-99.1\n<SEQUENCE>2\n<FILENAME>a12-18597_1ex99d1.htm\n<DESCRIPTION>EX-99.1\n<TEXT>\n\n\n<html>\n<head>\n\n  </head>\n<body lang=\"EN-US\">\n<div style=\"font-family:Times New Roman;\">\n<p align=\"right\" style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;text-align:right;\"><b><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-weight:bold;\">Exhibit 99.1</font></b></p>\n<p align=\"right\" style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;text-align:right;\"><b><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-weight:bold;\">&nbsp;</font></b></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\"><img width=\"283\" height=\"61\" src=\"g185971mmi001.jpg\"></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p align=\"right\" style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;text-align:right;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">August&nbsp;17, 2012</font></p>\n<p align=\"right\" style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;text-align:right;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">Dear Shareholders,</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">Please find below the El Gallo Complex development update.</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">Key development highlights over the past two weeks are:</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt .25in;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Symbol\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&#183;</font><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\"> Crushers ramping up towards designed capacity<br>  </font><font size=\"2\" face=\"Symbol\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&#183;</font><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\"> Piping installed for the heap leach pad<b><br>  </b></font><font size=\"2\" face=\"Symbol\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&#183;</font><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\"> 25,000 tonnes of material loaded onto heap leach pad<br>  </font><font size=\"2\" face=\"Symbol\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&#183;</font><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\"> New access ramp for Sagrado Corazon deposit completed<br>  </font><font size=\"2\" face=\"Symbol\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&#183;</font><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\"> Diesel generators at the process plant are ready to go</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt .25in;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">To view the El Gallo Development Photo Update, please click <u>here</u>.</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt;\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;width:100.0%;\">\n<tr>\n<td width=\"50%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:0in 0in 0in 0in;width:50.0%;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in .0001pt .25in;\"><b><i><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-style:italic;font-weight:bold;\">For further information contact:</font></i></b></p>    </td>\n<td width=\"50%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:0in 0in 0in 0in;width:50.0%;\">\n<p style=\"margi